<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>UCM Visas and Requirements</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <h1>UCM Visas and Requirements</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Visa Types</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Tourist Visa:</strong> For tourism, vacation, or visiting friends/family.</li>
                            <li><strong>Business Visa:</strong> For business-related activities such as meetings, conferences, or negotiations.</li>
                            <li><strong>Work Visa:</strong> For employment purposes. Different types of work visas are available depending on the nature of the job.</li>
                            <li><strong>Student Visa:</strong> For studying at accredited educational institutions in the US.</li>
                            <li><strong>Immigrant Visa:</strong> For permanent residency in the US.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Requirements</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Valid passport</li>
                            <li>Completed visa application form</li>
                            <li>Payment of visa fees</li>
                            <li>Evidence of ties to your home country</li>
                            <li>Proof of sufficient funds to cover your expenses during your stay</li>
                            <li>Additional documents depending on the visa type (such as invitation letters, employment contracts, or proof of enrollment)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-center">
            It's important to carefully review the specific requirements for the visa you're applying for and to apply well in advance of your intended travel dates.
        </p>
    </div>

</body>
